More than a dozen women and children have been killed in a graveyard in Afghansitan while paying their respects to dead relatives.

A bomb exploded today in the cemetery in a rural district of Nangarhar province, in the east of the country.

14 people were killed in the attack, which appeared to be timed to coincide with the festival of Eid ul-Fitr, marking the end of Ramadan.

